@NODE "Mail.0" "Re: Zip Gadget"
From: Marc Le Douarain <mavati@club-internet.fr>
Date: Sat, 28 Mar 1998 17:14:21 +0100
Subject: Re: Zip Gadget


>> How can I give my Blitz window a zip gadget while not allowing user
>> window sizing. I want to minimise my window to it's title bar *only*.

Well, I have tried these but I can't reduce nearly the window to the title
bar.
Perhaps it's totally not a good way, but let's have a look...


WbToScreen 0

FONT_YSIZE=11
LEFT=30
TOP=50
WIDTH=400
HEIGHT=200

SizeLimits WIDTH,FONT_YSIZE+8,WIDTH,HEIGHT
Window 0,LEFT,TOP,WIDTH,HEIGHT,$2020140e,"ZipWindowTest",1,2
Repeat
Until WaitEvent=$200
End



-- 

   Marc Le Douarain        < mavati@club-internet.fr>
             "Billou, on aura ta peau!"



@ENDNODE
@NODE "Mail.1" "Zip Gadget"
