From: Curt Esser <camge@ix.netcom.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Mar 1998 20:17:54 -0600
Subject: Re: Tokenized

Hi Paul,

On 10-Mar-98, Paul Burkey wrote:
>Hi,

>Does anyone know the format of the Blitz source file? I've
>written a program that scans through the ascii version of a
>Blitz program and it cretes statistics based on the commands
>and libraries used. 
>I think it'll be very usefull to help track down the libs
