From: Curt Esser <camge@ix.netcom.com>
Date: Mon, 02 Mar 1998 06:29:34 -0600
Subject: Re: Textfit_

Hi Paul,

On 01-Mar-98, Paul Burkey wrote:
>Hi Curt,
> 
>> maxchars.w=TextFit_(RastPort(0),&t$,chars,al.textEX,0,1,txlim,fsize)

>This is the first I've heard of TextFit_() but my first idea
