I tried this, and it still wouldn't work.  And then I realized I had used
windowfont on the wrong window!  Once I fixed this, it works fine.

Thanks for the advice.

BTW, Textfit_ returns the maximum characters of the window's font that will
fit into the specified rectangle - most useful for word-wrapping.  

Bye...
