thats seems very unfair from guildhall, dont you have a chance going 
through court with them ?

> 
> Q. Do you own the rights to Blitz Basic?
> A. No. We have no ownership of the current (or future)
> version of Blitz Basic. Acid gave us the source code
> with a view to us enhancing it (as we did with SuperTED)
> and working with them on a Blitz 3. This plan died
