          7 Mar 98 18:08:44 +0000
From: "S.J.CROY" <ap6013@qmw.ac.uk>
Date: Sat, 7 Mar 1998 18:08:10 +0000
Subject: Rotating Starfield

Hi all,

After reading my email about a rotating starfield, I guess Im just 
like all physics students - hopeless at explaining my ideas to 
everyone else :( To make up for it, Ive attached a working example of 
such a rotating starfield.
It`s even NTSC friendly so our American cousins can join in the fun 
:)
Hope this sorts you out

Cya
Steven



@ENDNODE
