is this:

*Array already Dim'd:* An array may not be re-defined

so why does this work with no problems....

Dim name.s(3)

name(0)="Paul"
name(1)="Curt"
name(2)="Bob"
name(3)="James"

Dim name.s(1)

name(0)="Paul"
name(1)="Curt"

Dim name.s(4)

name(0)="Paul"
name(1)="Curt"
name(2)="Bob"
name(3)="James"
name(4)="Peter"

Cheers,

Paul

