> =

> The more features we 'lend' from C the easier it'll be to port from
> one to the other. If we can keep Blitz's simplicity and it's solid
> traditional syntax (For..Next While...Wend etc..) then we can't
> go wrong.

    Agree...

    Regards,

        Fred

