@NODE "Mail.253" "Re[2]: BitplanesBitmap....this is getting on my tits!!!"
From: Paul Burkey <burkey@bigfoot.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Mar 1998 13:10:00 +0100
Subject: Re[2]: BitplanesBitmap....this is getting on my tits!!!

Hi Sami,
 
> BitPlanesBitmap db,6,%1111111 so you can render the shadow only once
> and the original graphics can be rendered without altering the shadow

That is how you would make a 7 plane bitmpap, To make a 1 plane bitmap
you'd use %10000000 which is hat you'll need if you want to render
shadow effects.
 
> The only drawback is (I think ) that it works VERY slowly on the GFX-cards.

Bitmaps won't work with GFX cards anyway so it's not an issue.

Cheers,

Paul

