@NODE "Mail.292" "Re: Print text letter by letter..."
    18 Mar 98 10:43:04 0
From: "David Mcminn" <MD.BE4.Student.eee.rgu.ac.uk@eee-student.eee.rgu.ac.uk>
Date: Wed, 18 Mar 1998 10:42:28 GMT0BST
Subject: Re: Print text letter by letter...

On 18 Mar 98 at 12:39, Tommi Nieminen spewed forth:

> How can i make text appear on a window letter by letter, like somebody 
> would be typing it?

Do something like this (assuming that you already have your window 
open etc):

a$="This is the text to print"
for i.w = 1 to len(a$)
  print mid$(a$,i,1)
  delay_ 10		; Wait for 10 50ths(?) of a second
next


Farewell, for now,

.oO David McMinn Oo.
