> commands to open one?

 I want to try using OS commands for opening windows and such, but 
possibly use Blitz commands for GTGadgets, which you'd probably need 
the blitz window structure filled in.
 I've used the OS GTGadget routines and would use them for more 
complex stuff, but if I'm writing a simple program then I'd probably 
prefer to use the Blitz GTgadget commands.


