>should be a Pheonix shared library or message port, so Ted (or any editor)
can
>easily get Pheonix to tokenise the source code, compile, stuff like that.  So
>I think we should wait till we have sorted out how Pheonix will work before
>jumping in to write an integrated editor.

>>  Seriously, we just need to make the new editor so good that everyone finds
