@NODE "Mail.395" "New ChunkyCPU Blit command planned"
Date: Tue, 31 Mar 1998 10:35:31 +0100
From: James Marshall <homegrown@eclipse.co.uk>
Subject: New ChunkyCPU Blit command planned

Hi,
  just to say I'm starting work on a ChunkyCPU equivalent of the BBlit
and UnBuffer commands. Maybe a few of us can collaborate on these type
of commands to produce a library... Christos Dimitrakakis posted to this
list that he was going to have a go implementing a library. Anyone else
got anything to contribute to it? New code/optimisation of my code,
etc.?
    James

