    since      |  __| '__/ _ \/ _ \  _   | |/ _` |/ __| |/ /   AMIGA
               | |  | | |  __/  __/ | |__| | (_| | (__|   <
        1987   |_|  |_|  \___|\___|  \____/ \__,_|\___|_|\_\        4
                 http://www.geocities.com/TimesSquare/5123/          ever



