Right..... hmmm.... this is just a kind of "educated" guess, but just before
your program ends, put the error number into d0, like this:

   ... your prog...

   MOVE.l  #5,d0
   End


Change the five in #5 to whatever number you want returning.

I'm not sure if this'll work (depends if the #End# command messes up d0 or
not), but it's worth a try! :)

