On 31-Mar-98, James Marshall wrote:
 
>So, as you can see, my routines are generally 50+% faster than their
>blitter counterparts on an 030@50Mhz. The results showing cpu_clipblit
>to be slightly faster than cpu_blit were surprising considering the
>extra computation required, but I confirmed the results with an
>additional run of 10000 blits.
