i search to program a procedure in blitz that simplify midi message to
input and to output (like the instruction "out3 with midi octets"( for
ex. out3 144,75,75 do a note on on the first channel) with the atari
st's gfa basic program)

i wish to have this procedure using (in preference order):
blueribbon.library (i search for the .fd and the references)
camd.library
midi.library
if anyone know how to perform, please email me
thanks

