and the valuable info continued...  :)


you should make your shapes to use 128 colors (7 bitplanes) and then
setting another bitplanesbitmap like this:

BitPlanesBitmap db,6,%1111111 so you can render the shadow only once
and the original graphics can be rendered without altering the shadow

in this way you can create spotlights very easy and fast!
The only drawback is (I think ) that it works VERY slowly on the GFX-card=
s. :(

