	enclosed is an example of the Bitplanesbitmap command working!
(*cheer from the crowd*).
	In response to whoever said that the way to create spotlight
effects saying that you create 7 bitplane objects to acheive this, you
actually only need one bitplane objects again, but you swap the
dark/light segments of the palette over. Anyway, enjoy this example.
