| A1200/28Mhz/2+4Mb/K56Flex/HyperCOM | Amiga Blitz 2 coder type UK bloke! |
| EMAIL: BootBlock@GeoCities.com     | www.geocities.com/SiliconValley/   |
| "NiteLife BBS" - online VERY sOOn! | Lab/4868/index.html - kind'a ready |
