be able to send or recieve a small example binary or blitz library right
with the message rather than go thru the rather large hassle of having to
make a special trip somewhere else to get it and have to hunt for it there.

  Might I suggest that we set a suggested size limit for attachements which
is not totally set in concrete if someone really believes that a reasonably
longer binary will be useful to a significant number of subscribers.
