Date: 28 Mar 98 06:35:29 +0000
Subject: Acidlibs Doc's

I have just downloaded update arcive of acidlibs.  Are there any doc's
on the new commands?  If there are not how  can I find out what
commands are in acidlibs?  Everything I use to scan libs to find out
the commands doesn't do acidlibs?

How do you use the FrontScreen command?

