--BOUNDARY.1748844304.5

Hi Andrew,

> How do you use the FrontScreen command?

Same as ActiveScreen.

I don't think there are any documents for the updated acidlibs
but they all have the usual online-help info as seen in BSS.

I've attached a very usefull file to hi email. It contains a list
of the Acidlibs commands collected into groups. It contains the
Syntax descriptions for all commands.

Cheers

-- 
